{"tid":829644,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"新疆伊犁 內一望無際的薰衣草!! 😍😍😍😍","createTime":"2018-09-20T15:12:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-23T05:13:58.000Z","uid":197098,"like":8,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b6bf6f581300107714556d91fd0e50f85f614e95","tid":829644,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T15:12:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">新疆的一個城市叫: 伊犁，它的總面積是278,851.95 km&sup2;，而香港總面積2,755.03 km&sup2;。這個城市比香港大一千多倍，這裡可看到漫山遍野的草原，遠遠看去好似一副油畫。森林茂密，花卉分呈，带来了瑰麗與浪漫，吸引着無数貪享自然之美的旅行者。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>請欣賞以下的照片：</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/20/230842_83b5009e040969ee7b60362ad7426573.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F20%2F230842_83b5009e040969ee7b60362ad7426573.jpeg&h=add55e34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/20/230851_ea571676ce9b75b0730a5d56350ae93e.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F20%2F230851_ea571676ce9b75b0730a5d56350ae93e.jpeg&h=2df13ea4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/20/230857_182845aceb39c9e413e28fd549058cf8.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F20%2F230857_182845aceb39c9e413e28fd549058cf8.jpeg&h=eaa6abfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/20/230903_9679ccb5a92f650b83fcf29e0a6a6775.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F20%2F230903_9679ccb5a92f650b83fcf29e0a6a6775.jpeg&h=79213821&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/20/230909_ddf9c9a45551e218c4018d5c53e9f6bb.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F20%2F23